Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:32.14,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,佐佐木~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:34.89,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,哦，辛苦了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:37.29,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,搞毛啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:41.06,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,楼下吸烟室没看到你人\N害我好找。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:44.91,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊抱歉，找我有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.22,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,部长说等会儿开会。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:00:58.33,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,啧。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:04.85,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,得，又要开那种\N屁都决定不了的会了。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.68,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,行啦行啦。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:09.72,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,唉……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:17.95,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,好想回家啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:25.64,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,懂你。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:06.54,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an9\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H8B8C89&\3c&HFAF7F3&}Genki Trading
