Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.60,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,谢谢光临~欢迎下次再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.55,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,欢迎光临！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:35.34,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,积分卡有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.19,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,有，给。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.07,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:42.89,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,卡还给您。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.58,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,袋子需要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.76,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,要个3日元的。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.71,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,加上袋子一共883日元。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.71,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,给。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.99,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,找零和收据。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.06,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,谢了。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.70,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,谢谢光临~欢迎下次再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.74,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\t(25,2235,\fscx109.48\fscy109.48)\blur0.3\fs9\c&H434343&\frz-5.26\fax0.05\move(294.5,151,292.42,149.67,25,2235)}Served By: Yamada
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.12,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,二号收银台的山田小姐……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:28.62,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,就是我下班后的治愈源泉。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:32.50,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,话是这么说……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:37.31,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,最近啥也不买也\N老往那儿跑。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.75,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,真是有病。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:43.36,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,要不干脆把这个\N当伴手礼送给山田小姐。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.72,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,说不定她还挺高兴。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.43,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fad(362,188)\fs12\bord2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H282C41&\3c&HF0F3F6&\pos(160,196)}Yummy Mochi Chips
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.07,DefaultItalics,YAMADA,0,0,0,,哇，太谢谢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:58.11,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我这不就跟新闻里那些\N妄想中年犯一个德性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:02.40,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs20\an9\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\c&H7C7B78&\3c&HFAF7F3&}Genki Trading
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:02.40,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,佐佐木君，你这算怎么回事？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:06.66,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,你以为「跑外勤」就是\N出去散步闲逛吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:10.71,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,真是的！不跟我汇报\N这是大问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:12.29,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,非常抱歉。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.92,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,你的汇报联络完全不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:18.18,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,连我的管理能力都\N要被怀疑了——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:22.30,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,部长打扰一下，\N四物公司的江田先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:24.94,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,来问报价的事怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:28.18,Default,CHIEF,0,0,0,,啊！说明天发过去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.75,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,让您久等了！抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.14,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,好的，明天一定发！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.52,Default,SUZUKI,0,0,0,,当然！非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.56,DefaultOverlap,CHIEF,0,0,0,,7点开会——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.64,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那个白痴上司……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.26,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,会开到半夜就算了，
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.53,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,结果屁都没定下来。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.57,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,宰了他……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.62,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,说着玩的。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.58,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,这种时候……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.67,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,就得这时候去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.76,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,今晚就去见山田小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.84,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,找零给您。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.67,Signs,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\fs36\fnArial Black\c&H4C5A50&\pos(145,219)\fscx10\t(20,186,\fscx100)\t(\fsp3)}droop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.67,Default,OHNO,0,0,0,,谢谢，欢迎下次再来。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.43,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,谢谢。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:15.23,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,山田小姐今天休息吗\N还是已经下班了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.94,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,今天真是什么都不顺啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.29,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,得靠尼古丁撑一撑了。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.44,Default,WOMEN,0,0,0,,哇，看那个人。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.93,Default,WOMEN,0,0,0,,好恶心。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:39.21,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,难道这里也没吸烟区？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.87,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.05,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,现在抽烟的人\N这么没人权了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.71,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,大叔。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.49,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,这边这边。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:56.72,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,这里的话可以抽哦。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.73,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我去，这也太诱人了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:03.71,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,等等，这里是超市后面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.57,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,让外人用这里\N不会被骂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:14.87,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,放心，谁来谁走\N根本没人管。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.70,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那我就不客气了。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.40,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,请便请便。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:37.08,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,搞不懂那是什么表情，
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.02,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但真是一张\N存在感很强的脸啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:42.93,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,完全不像个超市员工啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:51.53,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那个，小姐你是哪个区的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.16,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,借个火。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.04,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,叫你过来就是要这个。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.37,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,你倒是早说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.92,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,抱歉，稍微皮了一下。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.68,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,头一回见面别皮行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:19.51,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,大叔你就是\N总排二号收银台的人吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:25.27,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊？有吗？巧合吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.90,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,巧合？别的窗口空着也\N特意去那儿排是巧合？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.65,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,全被看穿了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.66,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,喜欢山田小姐对吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.96,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,她明知道还故意逗我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:41.61,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我懂。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.61,0:10:43.70,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,山田小姐确实好嘛。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.62,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,又可爱胸又大，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.40,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,还看着像没男朋友\N想想就让人心花怒放。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.92,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,那不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:56.68,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,确实，我是会特意\N去她那儿排队的怪人，
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:00.81,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,但那只是因为看着\N那丫头工作我就会莫名有干劲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:03.83,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我开心的就那一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.56,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,我、我太激动了。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.32,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不好意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.76,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,放心了。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:19.07,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,我还以为又有个傻逼顾客\N缠上山田小姐了。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:23.09,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,打着那种主意来搭讪的\N傻逼太多了。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:27.91,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,不过，大叔你不一样呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:34.26,Default,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,保持住你的绅士风度哦，\N佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:41.48,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,本来以为是那种\N爱拿大叔开涮的呛人小姑娘，
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:44.39,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,结果是个会关心同事的\N好孩子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.07,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.20,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,不好意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.40,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不好意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.66,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,那个，佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.66,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,诶？你、你怎么知道我名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.56,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,积分卡上看到的。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.31,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.04,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,一直谢谢您了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:16.75,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,我从田山酱那儿听说了，\N真的很开心。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:17.47,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:20.49,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,她说你是我的粉丝。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:23.59,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,东西掉了哦。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.88,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,不好意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.81,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,谢谢，欢迎下次再来。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.09,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,靠！田山！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.86,DefaultItalics,SASAKI,0,0,0,,记住你名字了\N你给我等着！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.07,DefaultItalics,TAYAMA,0,0,0,,你好你好，我是田山~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.08,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,下次也来吸烟区哦，
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:49.50,Default,YAMADA,0,0,0,,佐佐木先生。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:54.09,Default,SASAKI,0,0,0,,话说田山小姐\N是怎么知道我名字的啊？
